this project is designed to provide a web interface for an automated
watering system.
The web page will display 
    -Time
    -Date
    -watering status
    -Soil moisture content
    -humidity
    -temp of the sun
    -air temp
    -A graph of the past 7 days
        -temperature through eachday
        -when watering occured
        -and a meaasure of the soil mositure content through each day
 
The page will have several configurable parameters:
    -The number of watering events
    -The length of time an event should last
    -Overriding the status of the system
        -Switching it off or on permamnently. Manual operation.

 
